snippet.title: Alanah Pearce
snippet.description: Hi, I'm Alanah Pearce, I'm a 27 year old Australian living in California. I am a video game writer at Sony's Santa Monica Studio, and wrote *about* video games for various media outlets for nine years before that. Basically, this is my personal channel, which is a hobby that I update in my spare time. Even though it *is* intended to be a personal channel, I apparently end up talking about video games majority of the time anyway.
